     ventilation efficiency (Vou)."
  HELP
    ""
  INPUTCLASS 
    NotInput
  UNITS 
    cfm
  REPORTPRECISION
    0
  DEFAULT
    SumRevRef( ThrmlZn:VentSysRef, ThrmlZn:VentFlowWithMult ) / Cnt
